title: Looking For A Ranked Team
body:
Hey all, names Dan or Dust where every you prefer.
as you can see i'm looking for a ranked team, i want to start taking league team play more serious.
i can play mid at a higher level than most i VS but like some i am stuck in bronze, i have teams-speech and Skype for communication
add me on league if you have any interest, DuSt235.

replies.body: Just a heads up dont put "i play like a gold, but i'm bronze" It sort of makes you look like a tool..
Let my join you man I am climbing my way out of bronze. Right now on a winning spree 55% win ratio.
I was stuck in Bronze but I got out I have had some people say I play like a gold at times but I'm not worthy of being called that till I get gold so don't say you play like a gold till you get it
